  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "Although our current results are still below ODS-v2/ODS-v1+DeepSeek-R1* (Alzubi et al., 2025b), MA-RAG outperforms ODS-v1+Llama3.1-70B (Alzubi et al., 2025b).",
    "We believe that the performance gap largely depends on the reasoning model used.",
    "Additionally, we highlight that Perplexity Deep Research is a closed-source system without an arXiv paper or public report.",
    "These findings suggest that MA-RAG's combination of multi-agent reasoning and web integration is also highly effective for open-domain factual QA.",
    "A.5 WORKFLOWS We implement MA-RAG using LangChain and LangGraph 3, where agents communicate through structured JSON messages."
